{"sha": "fe57ab7c6414bbef66097c972e613492b8d95065", "node_id": "C_kwDOAAsO6NoAKGZlNTdhYjdjNjQxNGJiZWY2NjA5N2M5NzJlNjEzNDkyYjhkOTUwNjU", "commit": {"author": {"name": "bors", "email": "bors@rust-lang.org", "date": "2022-10-23T15:08:47Z"}, "committer": {"name": "bors", "email": "bors@rust-lang.org", "date": "2022-10-23T15:08:47Z"}, "message": "Auto merge of #9630 - CatDevz:fix-aawr-lint, r=flip1995\n\nFix allow_attributes_without_reason applying to external crate macros\n\nPreviously the `clippy::allow_attributes_without_reason` lint would apply to external crate macros. Many macros in the Rust ecosystem include these `allow` attributes without adding a reason, making this lint pretty much unusable in any sizable Rust project.\n\nThis commit fixes that by adding a check to the lint if the attribute is from an external crate macro and returning early.\n\n```\nchangelog: [`allow_attributes_without_reason`]: allow_attributes_without_reason no longer applies to external crate macros\n```", "tree": {"sha": "f96b195c4bebca37e21588baac4e120f8e7aa154", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/git/trees/f96b195c4bebca37e21588baac4e120f8e7aa154"}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/git/commits/fe57ab7c6414bbef66097c972e613492b8d95065", "comment_count": 0, "verification": {"verified": false, "reason": "unsigned", "signature": null, "payload": null}}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/commits/fe57ab7c6414bbef66097c972e613492b8d95065", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/commit/fe57ab7c6414bbef66097c972e613492b8d95065", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/commits/fe57ab7c6414bbef66097c972e613492b8d95065/comments", "author": {"login": "bors", "id": 3372342, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjMzNzIzNDI=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/3372342?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors", "html_url": "https://github.com/bors", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/u